item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: Well in all fairness, what allowed me to find all these restaurants was withdrawing from the tournament; so I think it's totally understandable that you zeroed in on a few places. The foodie in me is too ravenous for me to not venture out into NY when I know so much good food it around me. Haha. If I get to go, I'm sure a few pictures of the college campus cafeteria food will most likely be gracing the series yet again. After all, for me, the food is a big part of travel!

item.title: By: Terri Schurter
item.dc:creator: Terri Schurter
item.description: You did much better with finding good food than I did. I pretty much zeroed in on a couple of places. I should have been more adventurous. We won't have these options next year in Minneapolis. I'll look forward to your photographs of college campus cafeteria food in your Congress recap posts. :-) Maybe we will be lucky and have a congress in NYC again soon.
